      <title>据消息人士称，贝恩资本正在洽谈收购 Little Caesars 运营商 Sizzling Platter</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bain-capital-talks-buy-little-caesars-operator-sizzling-platter-sources-say-2024-12-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士周二表示，私募股权公司贝恩资本 (Bain Capital) 正在洽谈收购 Sizzling Platter，后者经营着 Little Caesars 和 Jersey Mike&#39;s 等餐厅特许经营权，交易价格超过 10 亿美元，包括债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/bain-capital-talks-buy-little-caesars-operator-sizzling-platter-sources-say-2024-12-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 22:37:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
